==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#{{geometry}} a [[polygon]] with nine sides; a [[nonagon]].

====Synonyms====
*[[nonagon]]

====Usage notes====
*While '''enneagon''' is etymologically consistent with [[pentagon]], [[hexagon]], etc. in that it uses a Greek prefix and suffix as opposed to a Latin prefix and a Greek suffix, it is rarely used; '''nonagon''' is the preferred term.

